<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <title>New Parcel Assignment</title>
</head>
<body style="font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; max-width: 600px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 20px; background-color: #f8f9fa; color: #000000;">
<div style="background: linear-gradient(135deg, rgba(255,255,255,0.95) 0%, rgba(248,249,250,0.98) 100%); padding: 30px; border-radius: 8px; box-shadow: 0 10px 15px -3px rgba(128, 0, 32, 0.2); border: 1px solid rgba(128, 0, 32, 0.3);">
    <div style="text-align: center; margin-bottom: 20px;">
        <h1 style="color: #800020; font-size: 24px; font-weight: bold; margin: 0;">New Delivery Assignment</h1>
    </div>

    <p style="color: #000000; font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.5; margin-bottom: 15px;">Hi <%= driverName %>,</p>

    <p style="color: #000000; font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.5; margin-bottom: 15px;">You have been assigned a new parcel for delivery. Please review the details below and confirm pickup when ready. üöö</p>

    <div style="background-color: #f8f9fa; padding: 15px; border-radius: 5px; border: 1px solid rgba(128, 0, 32, 0.3); margin: 20px 0; font-family: 'Courier New', monospace; font-weight: bold; font-size: 16px; text-align: center; color: #800020;">
        Tracking Number: <%= trackingNumber %>
    </div>

    <div style="background-color: #f8f9fa; padding: 20px; border-radius: 5px; margin: 20px 0; border: 1px solid rgba(128, 0, 32, 0.3);">
        <div style="margin-bottom: 10px; padding-bottom: 10px; border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(128, 0, 32, 0.3);">
            <span style="font-weight: bold; color: #000000; min-width: 140px; display: inline-block;">From (Sender):</span>
            <span style="color: #000000;"><%= senderName %></span>
        </div>
        <div style="margin-bottom: 10px; padding-bottom: 10px; border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(128, 0, 32, 0.3);">
            <span style="font-weight: bold; color: #000000; min-width: 140px; display: inline-block;">To (Receiver):</span>
            <span style="color: #000000;"><%= receiverName %></span>
        </div>
        <div>
            <span style="font-weight: bold; color: #000000; min-width: 140px; display: inline-block;">Assignment Status:</span>
            <span style="color: #000000;"><span style="background-color: #c44569; color: #ffffff; padding: 4px 12px; border-radius: 12px; font-size: 12px; font-weight: bold; text-transform: uppercase;">‚óè New Assignment</span></span>
        </div>
    </div>

    <div style="background-color: #f8f9fa; padding: 20px; border-radius: 5px; margin: 20px 0; border-left: 4px solid #c44569;">
        <h3 style="margin: 0 0 10px 0; color: #800020; font-size: 18px;">üìã Next Steps:</h3>
        <ol style="margin: 0; padding-left: 20px; color: #000000; font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.5;">
            <li><strong>Login to your driver portal</strong> to view complete delivery details</li>
            <li><strong>Confirm parcel pickup</strong> from the origin location</li>
            <li><strong>Update delivery status</strong> as you progress through the route</li>
            <li><strong>Complete delivery</strong> and obtain recipient confirmation</li>
        </ol>
    </div>

    <div style="text-align: center;">
        <a href="<%= driverPortalUrl %>" style="display: inline-block; background: linear-gradient(135deg, #800020 0%, #a00028 100%); color: #ffffff; padding: 12px 24px; text-decoration: none; border-radius: 5px; margin-top: 20px; font-weight: bold; font-size: 16px; border: 1px solid rgba(128, 0, 32, 0.3); box-shadow: 0 4px 6px -1px rgba(128, 0, 32, 0.15); transition: background 0.3s ease;">Access Driver Portal</a>
    </div>

    <p style="color: #000000; font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.5; margin-top: 20px; margin-bottom: 15px;">Please ensure you have all necessary equipment and documentation before beginning the delivery process. Safe driving!</p>

    <div style="background-color: #f8f9fa; padding: 15px; border-radius: 5px; margin-top: 20px; border-left: 4px solid #c44569;">
        <strong style="color: #000000;">Driver Support:</strong><br>
        For any questions or assistance during delivery, contact our driver support team at
        <a href="mailto:<%= supportEmail %>" style="color: #c44569;"><%= supportEmail %></a>
    </div>
</div>

<div style="font-size: 12px; color: #6c757d; margin-top: 30px; text-align: center;">
    &copy; <%= new Date().getFullYear() %> <%= appName %>. All rights reserved.<br>
    Driver notification for tracking number <%= trackingNumber %>
</div>
</body>
</html>
